
### Variables 
@apiurl = http://localhost:3500/api
@tableName = usuarios_grupos

### GET usuarios_grupos
GET {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}} HTTP/1.1

###
GET {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}}/1

### GET todos os grupos que o usuário 1 participa
GET {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}}/todosgruposusuarioparticipa/3
Accept: application/json

### GET Verificar papel do usuário
GET {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}}/papel/3/5
Accept: application/json

###
POST {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}}
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8

{
    "id_usuario": 1,
    "id_grupo": 1,
    "papel": "admin"
 }

###

DELETE {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}}/5/1

###
PUT {{apiurl}}/{{tableName}}/1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8

{
    "id_usuario": 1,
    "id_grupo": 1,
    "papel": "teste atualizado"
 }
